hopobject.body: Will I be paid weekly or monthly? robert riesenberg md atlanta center for medical research The 19-year-old actor is currently under fire for lashing out against "Two and a Half Men," publicly blasting the series as "filth" and encouraging people to stop watching the popular sitcom. "If you watch 'Two and a Half Men,' please stop watching 'Two and a Half Men.' I'm on 'Two and a Half Men,' and I don't want to be on it," said Jones in a videotaped testimonial for the Forerunner Chronicles. The group is linked to the Voice of Prophecy Seventh-Day Adventist church in Los Angeles, where Jones worships. "Please stop watching it and filling your head with filth," Jones said.
